                  </persName>
             to any body? - There is no transfer by 
               <persName id="t17900915-37-person405">
                  John
                   Pierce
               <interp inst="t17900915-37-person405" type="surname" value="Pierce"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-37-person405" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-37-person405" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             to Papps.</p>
               <p>Is there any transfer by Papps to any body? - Not that I could find.</p>
               <p>Mr. Garrow. Now we will proceed to prove that 
               <persName id="t17900915-37-person406">
                  John
                   Pierce
               <interp inst="t17900915-37-person406" type="surname" value="Pierce"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-37-person406" type="given" value="John"></interp>
