                  </persName>
            , of 
               <persName id="t17900915-37-person407">
                  Barn
                   Elms
               <interp inst="t17900915-37-person407" type="surname" value="Elms"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-37-person407" type="given" value="Barn"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-37-person407" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , was at that time dead.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179009150056"></xptr>Mr. Knowlys. Did you examine for any person of the name of 
               <persName id="t17900915-37-person408">
                  James
                   Pierce
               <interp inst="t17900915-37-person408" type="surname" value="Pierce"></interp>
